## 3. Scope

### In scope (v2 UX)

| # | Modul | Deskripsi |
|---|-------|-----------|
| S1 | Daftar project BOM | Parity kolom ERP + import Excel + HPP FX |
| S2 | Produk | Panel identitas + item master ERP picker |
| S3 | Struktur | Tree MODUL/SUBMODUL/PART + visual |
| S4 | Container | Packing + kapasitas kontainer |
| S5 | Material | PART list + DATA BASE picker |
| S6 | Proses | Rekap + detail routing/WC |
| S7 | Summary | Kalkulasi per part + operasi |
| S8 | COGS | Waterfall + parity checklist |
| S9 | FOB Jurnal | Custom ERP lines + export |
| S10 | Master bridge | API ke `/purchasing/materials`, WC, routing |

### Out of scope (fase ini)

- Approval workflow ERP (`/manufacture/approval`)
- QC Packing module
- Knife / Raw ticket
- Full PLM / CAD

