## 5. User experience — alur target

```mermaid
journey
  title Alur BOM Design Baru (target terintegrasi)
  section Dashboard
    Buka daftar BOM: 5: User
    Buat / Import: 4: User
  section Editor
    Isi produk + master ERP: 4: User
    Struktur tree: 3: User
    Material + proses: 3: User
    Container + COGS: 4: User
  section Output
    Parity OK + Export: 5: User
```

### Prinsip UX (Design Baru vs ERP Lama)

| Prinsip | ERP Lama | Design Baru |
|---------|----------|-------------|
| Navigasi | Wizard linear 4 step | Tab bebas + product panel persist |
| Master | Modul sidebar terpisah | Modal + future API |
| Costing | Biaya per row komponen | Rollup + COGS waterfall |
| Preview | Expand row list | Visual graph + summary |
| Excel | Tidak native | Import + mirror + parity |

