## 7. Mapping wizard ERP → tab app

| ERP Wizard Step | Tab Design Baru | Action migrasi |
|-----------------|-----------------|----------------|
| 1 Produk Akhir | Product Panel + root MODUL | Map fields 1:1 |
| 2 Komponen | Tab Struktur | 5 grup kolom ERP → kolom struktur |
| 3 Sub Perakitan & Bahan Baku | Tab Material | SF/WF tambahan app |
| 4 Operasi | Tab Proses + Routing modal | Rekap kategori app+ |
| — | Container, Summary, COGS, FOB | **Pertahankan app** |

---

## 8. Risiko

| Risiko | Mitigasi |
|--------|----------|
| Master dummy ≠ ERP live | API bridge + flag environment |
| User bingung 2 sistem | Single entry dashboard ERP embed iframe / redirect |
| COGS gap complex products | Prioritas import Excel; wizard template |
| Performance picker 800+ SKU | Search + pagination API |

